videos.description: Tyrique Jones gets through Marquette defenders and finishes with a strong two-handed slam in the second half.
videos.headline: Xavier's Jones gets aggressive at the rim

videos.description: The Musketeers make the steal and Naji Marshall goes coast-to-coast for an easy layup in the second half against Marquette.
videos.headline: Xavier's steal sets up easy fast-break bucket

videos.description: Harry Froling finds space to twirl past Xavier defenders and hits a tricky layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Marquette's Froling shows patience for nice layup

videos.description: Paull Scruggs connects with Trevon Bluiett who knocks in a jumper from the left field to keep Muskateers ahead 74-68 in the second half.
videos.headline: Bluiett hits mid-range jumper to extend Xavier lead

videos.description: Andrew Rowsey knocks in a couple of long 3-pointers from the top of the key to tie the game 80-80 with less than 5 minutes left in the game.
videos.headline: Marquette's Rowsey sinks back-to-back triples to tie game
